
Ranger Help for: city
=====================

SUMMARY:    
The city is any area that has buildings or other humanoid-made structures.
These will be areas where many of the higher forms of life interact with
each other. Being devoid of almost all of its original nature elements,
the city terrain is a harsh place for Rangers. Most Rangers prefer to
stay out of cities and enjoy the wilderness. Most of a Ranger's nature
skills will not work here. Cities are all over the realms.

=============================================================================
SEE ALSO: Individual terrains

